overview:
JMD Pacific Pte Ltd was incorporated in 2004. We have since grown to become one of the leading corporate gifts company catering to both local and regional countries.

We specialised in customisation of wide range of corporate gifts to enhance our customers’ corporate image. With proven track records and backed by extensive experience, we pride ourselves of being able to provide excellent service, premium quality products within our customers’ budget and prompt delivery. Our customers include government agencies, bank, unions, MNCs, hotels, airlines, country clubs, school, etc.

Besides, being supplier and stockist of corporate gifts, JMD Pacific Pte Ltd recently set up a subsidiary called Axtro Sports providing high quality and innovative sports equipments to swimmers, triathletes, etc.

Axtro Sports is the exclusive distributor for many brands such as FINIS, De Soto Sports, Swimovate and more. For more information, please visit www.axtrosports.com.
